txt.en: Grun Curldock can be found at Trader's Wharf.\n\nYou should return to Grun Curldock with the fish you have collected.
'Now that is a good haul! We'll not go hungry tonight! Thank you for assisting the League, [placeholder].'
Return to Grun Curldock with the fish you have collected
The League of the Axe casts its nets into the waters of the Brandywine River, hoping for food.
Fishing nets can be found along the shores of the Brandywine, near Trader's Wharf.\n\nYou should collect fish from fishing nets for the League of the Axe.

'We're not going to get much work done on an empty stomach. The League needs to eat! That's why I cast some nets into the Brandywine River. The river should provide us with some good food each day.\n\n'Would you check on the nets for me? Collect any fish you find for me and League will be grateful.'
